name: Bajaj Pulsar NS 160
des: Bajaj Pulsar NS160 is a street bike available at a starting price of tk. 201000 in India. It is available in only 1 variant and 3 colours. The Bajaj Pulsar NS160 is powered by 160.3cc BS6 engine which develops a power of 17.03 bhp and a torque of 14.6 Nm.
